OL,3,CCouncils warn Chancellor of widespread
OL,4,Cbankruptcies without funding boost
OL,6,FCouncils say they are "staring down
OL,7,Fthe barrel" financially, as new
OL,8,Fanalysis suggests they will be limited
OL,9,Fto being "little more than care
OL,10,Fservices" by the end of this
OL,11,FParliament without a boost to
OL,12,Fresources.
OL,14,FIn another dire warning of the
OL,15,Fperilous state of local government
OL,16,Ffinances, the study found that without
OL,17,Fextra funding, ministers will have to
OL,18,F"radically rethink" councils'
OL,19,Fstatutory responsibilities.
