OL,3,CCouncils warn Chancellor of widespread
OL,4,Cbankruptcies without funding boost
OL,6,FIf they don't, potentially six in ten
OL,7,Fcounty and unitary authorities in
OL,8,Frural areas face declaring bankruptcy
OL,9,Fby 2028, the study says.
OL,11,FMinisters have repeatedly warned of
OL,12,Fdifficult choices because of a #22
OL,13,Fbillion black hole they say officials
OL,14,Fhave discovered in the public finances.
OL,16,FThis has fuelled concerns that
OL,17,FChancellor Rachel Reeves could stick
OL,18,Fwith spending plans which would
OL,19,Fprovide limited relief for under-
OL,20,Fpressure councils when she delivers
OL,21,Fher Budget on October 30.
