OL,3,CCouncils warn Chancellor of widespread
OL,4,Cbankruptcies without funding boost
OL,6,FDespite annual council tax increases
OL,7,Fover the past decade, the CCN said
OL,8,Fcouncils have been forced to
OL,9,Fprioritise services they are legally
OL,10,Frequired to provide.
OL,12,FThis has coincided with significant
OL,13,Freductions in spending on key services
OL,14,Fsuch as libraries, buses, road
OL,15,Fmaintenance, children's centres and
OL,16,Fyouth services.
