OL,3,CCouncils warn Chancellor of widespread
OL,4,Cbankruptcies without funding boost
OL,6,FHowever, with many councils now
OL,7,Fproviding close to statutory minimum
OL,8,Flevels in services, the CCN said a
OL,9,Fcontinuing focus of resources on care
OL,10,Fservices would "not be enough" and
OL,11,Fthreaten "their ability to remain
OL,12,Fsolvent unless their statutory
OL,13,Fobligations change".
OL,15,FThe CCN said county and rural unitary
OL,16,Fcouncils are facing the largest
OL,17,Fdeficits over this Parliament.
