OL,3,CCouncils warn Chancellor of widespread
OL,4,Cbankruptcies without funding boost
OL,6,FA CCN survey of chief executives at
OL,7,Fthese authorities found that without
OL,8,Fextra funding at a time when the
OL,9,Fprofile of statutory responsibilities
OL,10,Fremains the same, 16 councils could be
OL,11,Fat risk of declaring effective
OL,12,Fbankruptcy by 2026-27, with a further
OL,13,Fsix expected to follow in 2027-28.
OL,14,FThis amounts to 60% of the CCN's
OL,15,Fmembers.
OL,17,FThis scenario would have a significant
OL,18,Fimpact on the delivery of frontline
OL,19,Fservices to more than 16 million
OL,20,Fpeople in England, the CCN added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
