OL,3,CCouncils warn Chancellor of widespread
OL,4,Cbankruptcies without funding boost
OL,6,FBarry Lewis, CCN finance spokesman and
OL,7,Fvice-chairman, said many of the 800-
OL,8,Fplus services provided by councils are
OL,9,F"essential" to residents, and
OL,10,Fauthorities of "all shapes and sizes"
OL,11,Fface a "bleak financial outlook".
OL,13,FHe added: "To meet all their projected
OL,14,Fservice pressures, councils are
OL,15,Fstaring down the barrel of a #54
OL,16,Fbillion funding black hole.
