OL,6,F"This needs to happen urgently with a
OL,7,Fplan to be actioned within the next 18
OL,8,Fmonths, otherwise we risk undermining
OL,9,Fthe wide-ranging purpose of local
OL,10,Fgovernment and derailing the
OL,11,Fgovernment's mission-led approach to
OL,12,Fpublic-service reform and greater
OL,13,Fdevolution to councils," Mr Lewis said.
